	* src/mcs51/ralloc.c (mcs51_assignRegisters): Skip optimizing registers
	pushed if there are parameters passed on the stack. Also, a cleaner
	way to decide if r0/r1 should be pushed/popped. (Together they fix
	bug #918693)

